# signal-autoplan

Eliminates manual PLAN.tasks.yaml authoring. stdlib only, no deps.

## When to use
- After a design approval, generate tasks: `signalos signal-autoplan generate "Add rate limiting to API" --wave 11`
- Review what was planned: `signalos signal-autoplan list --wave 11`
